---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const updated = 'July 8, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="How evautopro.com uses cookies and similar technologies."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-14 lg:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tight mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">1. What Cookies Are</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files stored on your device by your browser. They help websites
          function and can be used to measure how a site is used.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">2. Cookies We Use</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">
          evautopro.com is a static informational website and sets no cookies of its own for tracking
          or advertising. Cookies you may encounter come from:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>
            <strong>Hosting and security</strong> — our hosting and content delivery provider
            (Cloudflare) may set technical cookies needed for security and performance.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embedded services</strong> — fonts are loaded from Google Fonts, and links to
            WhatsApp open the WhatsApp service, each governed by that provider's own policies.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">3. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          You can delete or block cookies in your browser settings at any time. Blocking technical
          cookies may affect how some parts of the site work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">4. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy:
          <a href="mailto:cai@evautopro.com" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">cai@evautopro.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
